	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />We know for sure that all VRAM/CHR-ROM fetches are still performed if only one layer (background or sprites) is disabled, don't we? As long as that's the case, MMC3's scanline counter will surely keep working when sprites are disabled.

		

		</td>
