	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just tested this. MottZilla and tokumaru are correct: so long as either the sprite display bit or background display bit in $2001 are set to 1, the MMC3 IRQ will fire.<br /><br />Thanks again everyone!

		

